title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I just want to see Evan in one scene of season 9, even if it's just reused footage or a picture of him on a wall to say he was in every season.

I keep sleeping thru all the AHS news here, I was/am sick. So the 1984 thing--slasher films? Nothing to do with the George Orwell book? I haven't really seen 80s slasher movies and the ones I have seen, meh...
I hope Angela Bassett portrays Tina Turner!
